{"tid":1575482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國擴大間諜指控 阿里巴巴騰訊華為中車等均中槍","createTime":"2019-09-17T01:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T14:55:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"31136e6273906cf14150c5c95c3eab942bc6884e","tid":1575482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"美國擴大間諜指控 阿里巴巴騰訊華為中車等均中槍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190916-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E8%BB%8A%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%A7%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190916-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%259D%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25A7%258D&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=8b704962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190916-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E8%BB%8A%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%A7%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n美國早前以威脅國家安全，封殺中國科技巨企華為。美國雜誌《石英》（Quartz）13日報道，華府官員近日指控阿里巴巴、騰訊及百度等科技企業可能為中國政府從事間諜活動，或擴大對中國科技的審查範圍。有觀察認為，被華府點名的中國企業可能更難在美國投資或從事商業活動。而且美國擔心中國地鐵產品含監控，要求美國企業公共資金禁買中國中車。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據東網今天報道稱，美國務院指阿里巴巴騰訊百度或從事間諜活動。據美國國務院安全與防擴散局助理國務卿福特（Christopher Ashley Ford）早前在華盛頓的一個會議上表示，華為、騰訊、中興、阿里巴巴及百度等巨企，不論在事實上或法律上，在某些重要方面或出於某種目的，充當中國的武器，幫助北京發展、建立和維護用作監察和控制社會的技術。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述福特指，只要中國政府要求協助，科技巨企無法拒絕。隨着中國科技巨企把產品及服務出口至世界其他地方，相關的人權及安全問題也隨之影響其他國家。福特的演講已發表在國務院的網站。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國一貫拒絕並否認美國的此類指控。<br />\n<br />\n據該報道說，對於福特的指控，華為發言人指華為遵守中國政府的法律及繳付相關稅款，與該企業在全球其他國家的情況一樣，強調沒有任何國家或政黨在華為擁有決策權，公司並非由外部勢力擁有。阿里巴巴對報道不予置評，騰訊、百度及中興拒絕回應。"},{"pid":"8219e5928c75185767d1428a4672af3a4699fb15","tid":1575482,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0153110d682b35b762942efd6bb486bbdad932a5","tid":1575482,"uid":23088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a980bb7896b428c9d10e8e23b4d6a10cb148584","tid":1575482,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"快d沒收資產"},{"pid":"26787d6d51d5be999c148221b1001c57eceebfc6","tid":1575482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ff05f31ef9ee918b5e2cdfc6a4ba98e3f05764","tid":1575482,"uid":36134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:26:37.000Z","msg":"阿里巴巴同騰訊都比習種收歸黨有啦<br />\n個指控完全係基於合理觀察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1b80f9e868a211056f08d21a727f4b7ee8825c","tid":1575482,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4ff05f31ef9ee918b5e2cdfc6a4ba98e3f05764","tid":1575482,"uid":36134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:26:37.000Z","msg":"阿里巴巴同騰訊都比習種收歸黨有啦<br />\n個指控完全係基於合理觀察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c